text: Diana Esther Nwaiwu (born 10 October 1973) is a Nigerian former football goalkeeper. She played for the Nigeria women's national football team. She was part of the team at the 1991 FIFA Women's World Cup. She also played at the 1995 FIFA Women's World Cup. She played for the Kakanfo Babes in Nigeria. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian footballers Category:1991 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:1995 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers
